Welcome to AHKontroller (With XInput) - JoyToMinecraft Release!
This is a Release Branch with just JoyToMinecraft.

Completly new to AutoHotkey?
1. Install AutoHotkey (Must support version 2)
2. Run joytoMinecraft.ahk with AutoHotkey
3. Press F10 to exit after you're done!

JoyToMinecraft (JTMC) v1.1 features:
*  Type: KeyboardKey(ControllerKey)
*  Movement: WASD(Left Stick) Space(A) R(B) Sprint(Click Left Stick)
*  Camera: Mouse(Right Stick), Fast(Hold down Right Stick)
*  Inventory: E(Y)
*  Slot Switching: 1234567890(L/R Shoulder (or Bumper))
*  Actions: MouseLClick(Right Trigger) MouseRClick(Left Trigger)
* 
* Not Yet Implemented:
* Better Shifting, Throw(Q), Offhand(Not on 1.8), InvSlot(DPad)
* Cheats: Autoclick, KeepHolding, LootAll

